{"tid":1468963,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【幫推】連登旅遊保諮詢站【教你點Claim錢】","createTime":"2019-08-13T23:42:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T03:13:49.000Z","uid":294513,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"15a90ddbef80b185640574b04cd9b4e7a6827a36","tid":1468963,"uid":294513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:42:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">咁多位巴打絲打你地好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢幾日小弟見到好多唔同既手足都有留言講<span style=\"color: red;\">唔知/唔識</span>點樣Claim份旅遊保<br />\n<br />\n呢兩個月大家都好攰，我衷心希望原本預定左去旅行既你地可以去個旅行放鬆下心情，就算真係去唔成都唔好因為呢場運動而蝕左錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有見及此，小弟決定係度解答所有關於旅遊保既問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n假如你係<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">因為航班取消左而去唔成旅行</span> 或<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">因為航班取消左而想改期去旅行</span> 或<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">因為入唔到禁區而上唔到飛機</span> 或<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">單純有旅遊保問題想問(例如唔知xxx呢個情況賠唔賠)</span>等等<br />\n<br />\n歡迎留言並將你既問題講低 我盡我最快既能力幫你搞掂佢<br />\n<br />\n另外付上小弟TG：<a href=\"http://t.me/ppfuckoff\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fppfuckoff&d=cw67THcQ8%2BNa%2BfcBlgGHU%2BQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=b23db411\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/ppfuckoff</a><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">鄭重承諾  絕不過問任何私人資料</span><br />\nTG搵我既話我會覆左先 近排上TG多過開連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />見諒</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">格式如下</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">買左邊間保險公司：<br />\n買左咩Plan：<br />\n幾號買：<br />\n想問啲咩：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">目前已幫幾位巴打處理左，如有需要我會直接填埋份Claim form參考版本比你照抄</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">快點輪姦我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />等你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"c34ddbbe3a9b95250691360c37353ddefbea1923","tid":1468963,"uid":294513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T00:06:49.000Z","msg":"邊個留下負皮走左去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fa15f3153dcb735236c5ff101188dfffd700d26","tid":1468963,"uid":294513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T00:20:35.000Z","msg":"幫自己推下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">保證不作出任何銷售行為</span></span>"},{"pid":"3287a07e7b306264b62171d2f486d18194aa3e99","tid":1468963,"uid":294513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:12:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbf4b8be654ac655202adb6d01901e4e866ba83a","tid":1468963,"uid":294513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:16:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17374336244e818eda42e2aad60226cd054956f8","tid":1468963,"uid":204921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:15:38.000Z","msg":"想問下8月尾飛<br />\n有咩係全包到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n驚有咩冬瓜豆腐<br />\n例如：flight cancel 同delay"},{"pid":"ea0cb523f912f0a30ebee9bdfdc8964d66d44324","tid":1468963,"uid":18635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:20:29.000Z","msg":"我1/9 飛 <br />\n怕機管局又出陰招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有咩包delay and cancel flight ?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b77e859689bdb4763f3bba11a1e8c1ea1741df0d","tid":146896