.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />去玩得開心啲<br />\n放鬆下心情對所有野都有幫助<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:34:02.000Z","msg":"仲有一段時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過太期待所以好緊張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:37:02.000Z","msg":"Plan好行程未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇事既！應該飛到冇問題"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:38:12.000Z","msg":"自己份人唔會plan行程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但第一次一腳踢自己搞啲嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee30ba15b56106ae69a17ba364a435668925fd4a","tid":1468963,"uid":76854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55aa4c83e1f5e0a2980c3e950e4de2a5d0517d89","tid":1468963,"uid":204921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b77e859689bdb4763f3bba11a1e8c1ea1741df0d","tid":1468963,"uid":294513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17374336244e818eda42e2aad60226cd054956f8","tid":1468963,"uid":204921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:15:38.000Z","msg":"想問下8月尾飛<br />\n有咩係全包到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n驚有咩冬瓜豆腐<br />\n例如：flight cancel 同delay"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:21:12.000Z","msg":"基本上所有旅遊保都包行程取消&amp;delay<br />\n但現時絕大部份保險公司都出左聲明<br />\n8月12號後先買旅遊保既客戶唔包因為香港出發唔到而取消既行程<br />\n不過點都好，旅遊保係一定要買，因為旅遊保仲保障左電話、行李、醫療(你係個邊病左就咁去睇門診醫生都包)、意外等等<br />\n呢幾日TG收到好多人問，但發現好多人都貪平多幾十蚊而買啲名都未聽過既公司，我個人真係唔建議。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:22:51.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔包就是但買fwd axa算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:47:50.000Z","msg":"問左fwd: 如果是8月12日及8月13日, 由於機管局的通知是&rdquo;機場受阻&rdquo; 而不是&rdquo;機場關閉&rdquo;, 因此不在保障範圍內。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}